name: Evander
description:
"Evander" from The "Insight" Collection by Armin Jabbarehasl is now available on hic et nunc.  
  
"Evander" is a Generative art that is made out of simple photographs from different objects to provide a generative piece.  
  
The Owner will receive the "Evander"'s High Resolution(1080 X 1080) File.
